    "methodology": "FMU case figures represent advice and support cases handled by the Forced Marriage Unit, jointly operated by the Home Office and FCDO. They do not represent total prevalence, which is widely believed to be substantially higher. Under-18 proportions are calculated from FMU case data. Forced Marriage Protection Order counts come from Ministry of Justice family court statistics. The 2020-21 drop reflects reduced reporting during COVID-19, not a reduction in forced marriages.",
